config.script:
TestID = self.view.custom.TestDetails.TestID
	StatusName = 'Approved'
	ChangedBy = self.session.props.auth.user.userName
	Message = 'Successfully approved the test!'
	if TestID > 0:
		mes.quality.sp.updateTestStatus(TestID, StatusName, ChangedBy)
		system.perspective.openPopup('Message', 'GlobalComponents/Modals/ErrorModal', params = {'ErrorMessage':Message, 'ModalName':'Test'})
	else:
		pass
	
	messageType = 'refreshQualityTable'
	payload = {}
	system.perspective.sendMessage(messageType, payload, view = 'session')

TestID = self.view.custom.TestDetails.TestID
